      <title>拜登创建两座国家纪念碑，保护 848,000 英亩土地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/biden-protects-848-000-acres-by-creating-two-national-monuments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据白宫称，总统乔·拜登将建立两座新的国家纪念碑，保护加州 848,000 英亩的土地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-07/biden-protects-848-000-acres-by-creating-two-national-monuments</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
